DECLARATIONBLOCK STATLIST INPUTNODE RETURN CONDITIONAL LOOP GENERIC_NODE 
PARAMBLOCK PRED UNARYOP SEPARATOR INVALIDTYPE BOOLEAN VOID ENDIF

